{"tid":142402,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖] 主人最愛嘅公仔爛左 求幫手","createTime":"2017-03-03T17:10:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-08T14:02:04.000Z","uid":88948,"like":36,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"478d02b52229c389025d99de98d67b20b53f8654","tid":142402,"uid":88948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T17:10:30.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n幾個月前帶主人返屋企嗰陣 愛協送埋呢隻公仔比我 話主人不嬲好中意同佢玩<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/04/004401_c28a16ac76bcaf00d3eedce4e0af3efa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F04%2F004401_c28a16ac76bcaf00d3eedce4e0af3efa.jpg&h=0af0f8b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最近佢咬到隻公仔爛哂 補左幾次都係咁樣<br />\n之前買過其他玩具 都冇乜點寵幸佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人係寵物店/玩具舖見過呢隻野?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/04/004530_02034c0175af5adb767583093b15a74b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F04%2F004530_02034c0175af5adb767583093b15a74b.jpg&h=16d611f4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AOCp9oK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAOCp9oK.jpg&h=c9e1e80e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/94NiK92.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F94NiK92.jpg&h=46159a18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n主人圖:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FxF369b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFxF369b.jpg&h=1755bb4b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6oE4d8q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6oE4d8q.jpg&h=32451b01&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rf5ZjX5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=ht