/>\n巴打領養返隻小熊貓啦<br />\n應該有好多玳瑁貓揾緊屋企架"},{"pid":"990cf83047d079b4063e65076f9cb3ec1092b859","tid":142402,"uid":88948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T19:29:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>爛左既位縫返得唔得 頂住先</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n已經唔太頂得住 補完一個窿好快又有第二個<br />\n我諗都係跟上面啲巴打嘅提議<br />\n一係加布遮住先 一係索性整件衫比件公仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係都幾大工程"},{"pid":"80a308b5a2de805c6148723b113bb15082c2fb07","tid":142402,"uid":3304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T19:32:50.000Z","msg":"講真我自己隻公仔陪咗我十幾年<br />\n你買過隻一模一樣嘅都唔係嗰隻啦<br />\n利申有幾隻同款公仔，係攬住嗰隻先瞓到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dfaecc8d9b84dfbec540fa67d0b5d29f4c85f67","tid":142402,"uid":88948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T19:35:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔好放棄隻公仔啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n貓仔一定好鍾意佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n爛都唔好拋呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點都會留係度 反而係驚佢呑左啲綿花落肚</blockquote><br />\n試下搵啲布料慢慢蓋過爛左嘅部分？<br />\n逐啲逐啲蓋貓仔可能唔覺<br />\n正如上面有人話可能係氣味問題<br />\n如果搵公仔醫生可能無左原本嘅氣味呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢啲彊屍牙真係好犀利<br />\n再爛落去嘅話 我諗要試下呢個方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n十幾年後貓仔百年歸老之後<br />\n你睇返呢隻公仔一定會諗起佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n完全唔敢諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望佢會快高長大然後長命百歲"},{"pid":"25a2d55d5637817ca95921c2e0590f07d42f3905","tid":142402,"uid":88948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T19:37:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最主要係陣味<br />\n你買同款同樣都冇用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我有諗過如果買到同款同樣<br />\n就試下將陣味捽落去新嗰隻度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知work唔work"},{"pid":"b8c9cd5a5b7ad9fcb99084666b7e9c5807391ee4","tid":142402,"uid":88948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T19:42:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講真我自己隻公仔陪咗我十幾年<br />\n你買過隻一模一樣嘅都唔係嗰隻啦<br />\n利申有幾隻同款公仔，係攬住嗰隻先瞓到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果揾到隻一模一樣嘅 有得比佢揀下黎咬都好<br />\n可能原本嗰隻唔會爛得咁快"},{"pid":"890638a1cbbb5602950ab49e10942da62ab09163","tid":142402,"uid":88948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T19:48:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買ikea老鼠</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n下次去ikea順便望下啲公仔先<br />\n不過呢隻老鼠好似太大<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/04/034741_5e66c27208b96fdb7ca639b95672bbea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F04%2F034741_5e66c27208b96fdb7ca639b95672bbea.jpg&h=27b04d9f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"102a7a88e8687619930953c20d2b67d4b580f029","tid":142402,"uid":50254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T21:04:52.000Z","msg":"點解咁似我隻貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nd8fyp6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnd8fyp6.jpg&h=cfabf545&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bc224fce7443710a62e9aef0a2868004229f2db6","tid":142402,"uid":59165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T21:21:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔好放棄隻公仔啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n貓仔一定好鍾意佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n爛都唔好拋呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點都會留係度 反而係驚佢呑左啲綿花落肚</blockquote><br />\n試下搵啲布料慢慢蓋過爛左嘅部分？<br />\n逐啲逐啲蓋貓仔可能唔覺<br />\n正如上面有人話可能係氣味問題<br />\n如果搵公仔醫生可能無左原本嘅氣味呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢啲彊屍牙真係好犀利<br />\n再爛落去嘅話 我諗要試下呢個方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n十幾年後貓仔百年歸老之後<br />\n你睇返呢隻公仔一定會諗起佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n完全唔敢諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望佢會快高長大然後長命百歲</blockquote><br />\n擔住佢走黎走去咁cute<br />\n我個隻咬爛完會呑左d布 痴線 又勁健康<br />\n我全部衫都比佢咬到穿哂洞 有次唔知仲著左出街<br />\n係d屎到搵返我塊布<br />\n連醫生都無辦法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5f351c8d637c7adc02618183d7aea8683d06099","tid":142402,"uid":33536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T21:23:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.ettoday.net/news/20170225/873968.htm?from=fb_et_pets\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20170225%2F873968.htm%3Ffrom%3Dfb_et_pets&d=JGY83BSksxqOTSpEwQoHnUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=5c6ab402\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ettoday.net/news/20170225/873968.htm?from=fb_et_pets</a>"},{"pid":"7e27094c618bbe0b721f807af017d60cdfe0a044","tid":142402,"uid":29846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T22:05:22.000Z","msg":"建議樓主整返好，唔好買過隻新<br />\n我都有張被攬咗廿幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 出世攬到而家<br />\n雖然爛撚哂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但就算買過張新都代替唔到的"}]}